@startuml 

!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontStyle bold

' 客户端
class "客户端\n(Menu/GameBoard)" as Client #LightBlue {
    简单调用外观类提供的方法
}

' 外观类
class MusicPlayer <<Facade>> #LightGreen {
    <b>简化的接口</b>
    --
    + play()
    + stop()
    + pause()
    + resume()
    + setVolume(volume)
    + playNext()
    + getMusicNames()
}

' 子系统
rectangle "复杂子系统\n(javax.sound.sampled)" #LightYellow {
    class AudioSystem
    class AudioInputStream
    class Clip
    class FloatControl
    class LineListener
    class LineEvent
}

Client --> MusicPlayer : 简单调用
MusicPlayer --> AudioSystem
MusicPlayer --> AudioInputStream
MusicPlayer --> Clip
MusicPlayer --> FloatControl
MusicPlayer --> LineListener

note right of MusicPlayer
    <b>外观模式的优点：</b>
    1. 简化客户端调用
    2. 隐藏子系统复杂性
    3. 降低耦合度
    4. 提供统一入口
end note

note bottom of Client
    客户端只需要调用:
    musicPlayer.play()
    musicPlayer.stop()
    等简单方法
end note

@enduml
